article_title: China Premier Li Keqiang: Beijing Has Tools to Pump Up Economy
article_text:
BEIJING—China’s premier said Beijing has the tools to boost the slowing economy if employment suffers and promised further constraints on government power so that the private sector can grow.

At his only scheduled news conference of the year, Premier Li Keqiang struck a reassuring tone about his government’s policies for managing the slowdown, deflation and other economic challenges. He also played down tensions with the U.S. and...
